OL,3,CArrests for illegal work at record
OL,4,Clevel as government increase
OL,5,Cdeportations
OL,7,FThe number of arrests for illegal
OL,8,Fworking has reached record highs as
OL,9,Fpolice ramp up visits to businesses
OL,10,Flike nail bars, car washes, barbers
OL,11,Fand takeaways suspected of employing
OL,12,Fpeople without the right to work in
OL,13,Fthe UK.
OL,15,FSome 12,791 visits took place in 2025,
OL,16,Fup 57% from 8,122 in the previous
OL,17,Fyear, to suspected businesses.
