OL,7,FMinisters are seeking to crack down on
OL,8,Fillegal working in the UK, as part of
OL,9,Fefforts to deter those coming to the
OL,10,Fcountry illegally.
OL,12,FThere were 8,971 arrests last year, up
OL,13,Fnearly 59% compared to 5,647 in 2024 `
OL,14,Fthe previous highest point in data
OL,15,Fpublished by the Home Office.
OL,17,FThe figures are the highest since the
OL,18,FHome Office began tracking them in
OL,19,F2019.
