OL,3,CArrests for illegal work at record
OL,4,Clevel as government increase
OL,5,Cdeportations
OL,7,FOf those arrested, 1,087 people have
OL,8,Fbeen removed from the UK so far.
OL,10,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood said:
OL,11,F"There is no place for illegal working
OL,12,Fin our communities.
OL,14,F"That is why we have surged
OL,15,Fenforcement activity to the highest
OL,16,Flevel in British history so illegal
OL,17,Fmigrants in the black economy have
OL,18,Fnowhere to hide.
OL,20,F"I will stop at nothing to restore
OL,21,Forder and control to our borders."
