OL,5,Cdeportations
OL,7,FThe Home Office also said visits were
OL,8,Fup 77% and arrests were up 83% since
OL,9,FLabour came to power.
OL,11,FSome 17,483 visits and 12,322 arrests
OL,12,Fwere recorded between July 2024 and
OL,13,FDecember last year, up from 9,894 and
OL,14,F6,725 respectively across January 2023
OL,15,Fto June 2024.
OL,17,FOf the arrests, 1,726 people have been
OL,18,Freturned so far, up 35% on the 1,283
OL,19,Fremoved from visits in the previous 18-
OL,20,Fmonth period.
