OL,7,FAmong visits by immigration
OL,8,Fenforcement, officers arrested 13
OL,9,Fpeople at a warehouse in Shoreham-by-
OL,10,FSea, West Sussex, on November 25 which
OL,11,Fled to 11 Brazilian and Romanian
OL,12,Fnationals being detained for removal
OL,13,Ffrom the UK.
OL,15,FOn December 16, officers arrested 30
OL,16,FIndian and Albanian men at a
OL,17,Fconstruction site in Swindon,
OL,18,FWiltshire, the Home Office said,
OL,19,Fnearly all of whom were detained for
OL,20,Fremoval from the UK, including five
OL,21,Freleased on immigration bail.
